  "text": "This section provides an overview of the semantic augmentation strategies supported by the TC framework proposed in [CITATION_1] , and presents its extension to the category meta-graph. Examples for the various semantic features, feature combinations and semantic augmentation strategies employed for the entity Obama are provided in Table 4 .",
